data.description: *Back on market- no fault to seller* Seller has an ASSUMABLE VA LOAN 2.75% - Welcome home to this beautiful 3 bed/2 bath home tucked away in a neighborhood with no HOA! As you enter you are welcomed into the living room with vaulted ceilings which make the room feel large and inviting. Cozy up by the fireplace, creating the perfect spot to relax and unwind after a long day. The generously sized kitchen has extra countertop and cabinet space and a breakfast bar, with its own breakfast nook. The primary suite has a large ensuite master bath with a double vanity, separate shower and tub, and a walk-in closet! The primary suite also features a set of french doors that leads to the back patio. Step outside to the inviting back patio, complete with a custom-built bar which is a perfect spot to entertain your friends and cheer on your favorite sports team!On the colder nights, sit around the firepit, it's the perfect spot for entertaining and creating lasting memories! You don't want to miss out on this home! Roof Oct 2023, Gutters Nov 2023, HVAC July 2023, New microwave and dishwasher, seller installed backyard fence, 22 min to Hurlburt.
